Title: Deep Fried & Minty Fresh
Plot: Langston and Nick are called to investigate a murder at a fast food restaurant and have quite a task ahead of them when they discover that much of the evidence is coated in cooking oil.
GuestStars: David Berman, Liz Vassey, John Ales, Daniella Alonso, Pat Asanti, Drew Tyler Bell, Alex Carter, Dameon Clarke, Patricia Forte, Megan Hilty, Archie Kao, Alexandra Krosney, Sheeri Rappaport, Allison Scagliotti, Nik
